# Blacklist everything by default
*

# And allow directories (empty directories are not included)
!**/

### Blacklist specific things for specific reasons

# Generated by Cargo
# will have compiled files and executables
/target/

# These are backup files generated by rustfmt
**/*.rs.bk

### Now only Whitelist

# Git stuff
!/.gitignore
!/.gitattributes

# Github specific files
!/.github/*

# Meta Project Files
!/.meta/**/*

# IDEA specific run configurations
!/.run

# License files
!/LICENSE*

# Documentation files
!/README.md

# Build files
!/Cargo.toml
!/rustfmt.toml
!/.editorconfig

# Making an executable, so keep the lock file
!/Cargo.lock

# Rust Source files in `/src/`
!/src/**/*.rs
!/assets/**/*
!/config/**/*
# Don't include the autogenerate log4rs.yml logger configuration
config/log4rs.yml
!/docs/**/*
